61008145243/http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=27&hitYear=2016&termGbn=week|archivedate=2016-10-08}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=46&hitYear=2016&termGbn=week|title=Autumn Story}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=08&hitYear=2017&termGbn=week|title=Winter Dream}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=22&hitYear=2017&termGbn=week|title= Dream Part.01}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=44&hitYear=2017&termGbn=week|title=Dream Part.02}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=30&hitYear=2018&termGbn=week|title=Rise Up}}\n* {{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=47&hitYear=2019&termGbn=week|title=Blue Flame}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%\" |[[Oricon Albums Chart|JPN]]<br><ref name=\"JPN\">''Venus'': {{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/ja/w/2019-04-15/|script-title=ja:\u9031\u9593 CD\u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0 2019\u5e7404\u670815\u65e5\u4ed8|trans-title=Weekly CD Album Ranking on April 15, 2019|work=Oricon News|accessdate=April 10, 2019|language=ja}}\n* ''Blue Flame'': {{cite web|url=https://www.oricon.co.jp/rank/ja/w/2020-01-06/|script-title=ja:\u9031\u9593 CD\u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0 2020\u5e7401\u670806\u65e5\u4ed8|trans-title=Weekly CD Album Ranking on January 6, 2020|publisher=Oricon|accessdate=January 6, 2020|language=ja}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:90%\" |[[Billboard charts#Albums|US<br>{{small|World}}]]<br><ref>Billboard World Albums\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/world-albums/2016-03-12|title=Spring Up|date=2016-03-12|accessdate=2017-12-22}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/world-albums/2016-07-23|title=Summer Vibes|date=2016-07-23|accessdate=2017-12-22}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/world-albums/2016-12-03|title=Autumn Story|date=2016-12-03|accessdate=2017-12-22}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/world-albums/2017-06-17|title=Dream Part. 01|date=2017-07-17|accessdate=2017-12-22}}\n*{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/world-albums/2017-11-18|title=Dream Part. 02|date=2017-11-18|accessdate=2017-12-22}}\n*{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/world-albums/2018-08-04|title=Rise Up|date=2018-08-04|accessdate=2018-08-12}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| ''[[Spring Up]]''\n|\n*Released: February 23, 2016 {{small|(KOR)}}\n*Label: Fantagio Music\n*Formats: CD, download, streaming\n| 4 || \u2014 || 6\n|\n* KOR: 26,712<!--24,668 + 2,044--><ref name=\"gaonyear2016\">{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=&targetTime=2016&hitYear=2016&termGbn=year|title=2016\ub144 Album Chart|trans-title=2016 Album Chart|website=Gaon Music Chart|accessdate=January 12, 2019|language=ko}}</ref><ref name=\"gaonmar2017\">{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/album.gaon?termGbn=month&hitYear=2017&targetTime=03&nationGbn=K&year_time=|title=2017\ub144 03\uc6d4 Album Chart (\uad6d\ub0b4)|trans-title=March 2017 Album Chart (Domestic)|website=Gaon Music Chart|accessdate=January 12, 2019|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| ''[[Summer Vibes]]''\n|\n*Released: July 1, 2016 {{small|(KOR)}}\n*Label: Fantagio Music\n*Formats: CD, download, streaming\n| 2 || \u2014 || 6\n|\n* KOR: 31,077<!--29,907 + 988--><ref name=\"gaonyear2016\"/><ref name=\"gaonmar2017\"/>\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| ''[[Autumn Story (EP)|Autumn Story]]''\n|\n* Released: November 10, 2016 {{small|(KOR)}}\n* Label: Fantagio Music\n* Formats: CD, download, streaming\n| 