gital Song Sales|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/astro/chart-history/world-digital-song-sales|work=Billboard|access-date=August 28, 2019|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828065313/https://www.billboard.com/music/astro/chart-history/world-digital-song-sales|archivedate=August 28, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Hide & Seek\" <small>(\uc228\ubc14\uaf2d\uc9c8)</small>\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2016\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"row\"| ''Spring Up''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Breathless\" <small>(\uc228\uac00\ube60)</small>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || 21\n| ''Summer Vibes''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Confession\" <small>(\uace0\ubc31)</small>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| ''Autumn Story''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Again\" <small>(\ubd99\uc7a1\uc558\uc5b4\uc57c \ud574)</small>\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2017\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| ''Winter Dream''\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Baby\"\n| \u2014 || 2 || 24\n|''Dream Part.01''\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| \"Crazy Sexy Cool\"\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || 11\n| ''Dream Part.02''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Always You\" <small>(\ub108\uc796\uc544)</small>\n| 2018\n| \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Always You\" did not enter the Gaon Digital Chart, but appeared at number 95 on the component Download Chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=30&hitYear=2018&termGbn=week|script-title=ko:2018\ub144 28\uc8fc\ucc28 Download Chart|trans-title=Week 28 of 2018 Download Chart|website=Gaon Music Chart|accessdate=November 10, 2018|language=ko}}</ref>}} || \u2014 || \u2014\n| ''Rise Up''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"All Night\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2019\n| 154 || 38 || 6\n| ''All Light''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Blue Flame\"\n| \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Blue Flame\" did not enter the Gaon Digital Chart, but appeared at number 56 on the component Download Chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S10